{"id":25,"ayahs":[{"number":164,"arabic":"إِنَّ فِى خَلْقِ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَٱخْتِلَٰفِ ٱلَّيْلِ وَٱلنَّهَارِ وَٱلْفُلْكِ ٱلَّتِى تَجْرِى فِى ٱلْبَحْرِ بِمَا يَنفَعُ ٱلنَّاسَ وَمَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مِن مَّآءٍۢ فَأَحْيَا بِهِ ٱلْأَرْضَ بَعْدَ مَوْتِهَا وَبَثَّ فِيهَا مِن كُلِّ دَآبَّةٍۢ وَتَصْرِيفِ ٱلرِّيَٰحِ وَٱلسَّحَابِ ٱلْمُسَخَّرِ بَيْنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ لَءَايَٰتٍۢ لِّقَوْمٍۢ يَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"Verily, in the creation of the heavens and of the earth, and the succession of night and day: and in the ships that speed through the sea with what is useful to man: and in the waters which God sends down from the sky, giving life thereby to the earth after it had, been lifeless, and causing all manner of living creatures to multiply thereon: and in the change of the winds, and the clouds that run their appointed courses between sky and earth: [in all this] there are messages indeed for people who use their reason.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/171.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":82236,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82237,"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82238,"position":3,"arabic":"خَلْقِ","translation":"সৃষ্টির","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82239,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশ মন্ডলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82240,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82241,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱخْتِلَـٰفِ","translation":"ও পরিবর্তনের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82242,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلِ","translation":"রাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82243,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَ