position":40,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82276,"position":41,"arabic":"لَـَٔايَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"অবশ্যই নিদর্শনাদি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82277,"position":42,"arabic":"لِّقَوْمٍۢ","translation":"সম্প্রদায়ের জন্যে(রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_042.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82278,"position":43,"arabic":"يَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"(যারা) জ্ঞান রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_164_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82279,"position":44,"arabic":"١٦٤","translation":"(১৬৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":165,"arabic":"وَمِنَ ٱلنَّاسِ مَن يَتَّخِذُ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَندَادًۭا يُحِبُّونَهُمْ كَحُبِّ ٱللَّهِ ۖ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ أَشَدُّ حُبًّۭا لِّلَّهِ ۗ وَلَوْ يَرَى ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُوٓا۟ إِذْ يَرَوْنَ ٱلْعَذَابَ أَنَّ ٱلْقُوَّةَ لِلَّهِ جَمِيعًۭا وَأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ شَدِيدُ ٱلْعَذَابِ","translation":"And yet there are people who choose to believe in beings that allegedly rival God, loving them as [only] God should be loved: whereas those who have attained to faith love God more than all else. If they who are bent on evildoing could but see - as see they will when they are made to suffer [on Resurrection Day] -that all might belongs to God alone, and that God is severe in [meting out] punishment!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/172.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":82369,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","translation":"কিন্তু মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_165_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82370,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের (এমনও আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_165_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82371,"position":3,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_165_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82372,"position":4,"arabic":"يَتَّخِذُ","translation":"গ্রহণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_165_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82373,"position":5,"arabic":"